episodes.title: Manhattan Millionaires & the Cult who Controls them
episodes.description:
A cult that began in the 1970s still continues unchecked inside million-dollar penthouses attended by actors, artists, surgeons and lawyers. Allegations of forced arranged marriages, physical abuse, forced adoptions and coercion have been levelled against this cult since its inception. 
This is the story of the millionaires of Manhattan #manhattan #newyork #adamdriver #millionaremindset #celebrities #coversive control.
